OL,3,CHarry Potter first edition 'worth
OL,4,C#30k' found in rubbish
OL,6,FA first edition Harry Potter is
OL,7,Fexpected to fetch more than #30,000 at
OL,8,Fauction after being saved from rubbish.
OL,10,FThe rare copy of Harry Potter and the
OL,11,FPhilosopher's Stone was discovered at
OL,12,Fa property in Brixham.
OL,14,FIt had sat on the owner's bookshelf
OL,15,Ffor nearly 20 years, and was due to be
OL,16,Fthrown away after the he died.
