OL,6,FBut experts from NLB Auctions in
OL,7,FPaignton - invited by the owner's
OL,8,Ffamily to take a look at their
OL,9,Fbelongings - found the book in a
OL,10,Frubbish pile.
OL,12,F'It was bought for #2'
OL,14,FDaniel Pearce, who runs the auction
OL,15,Fhouse, said it was a lucky find.
OL,17,FHe told ITV News West Country: "People
OL,18,Fbin all sorts of stuff. Before we go
OL,19,Fin, we often say to people 'don't
OL,20,Fthrow anything away'.
