OL,6,F"This book was sat in a box, just
OL,7,Fwaiting to go out with the rubbish."
OL,9,FThere are thought to be 500 first
OL,10,Fedition copies of Harry Potter and the
OL,11,FPhilosopher's Stone in circulation -
OL,12,F200 were sent to bookshops and 300
OL,13,Fwere sent to libraries.
OL,15,FThis version was originally sent to a
OL,16,Flibrary and later bought by a private
OL,17,Fowner for #2.
OL,19,FDaniel said: "We don't know how many
OL,20,Ftimes it may have changed hands.
